Hungarian lender OTP Bank Nyrt
opened an OTP Credit branch in  Ukraine  to revive interest in
consumer loans.  OTP Credit, which started working on March 18, already
operates in six Ukrainian cities, the bank said in e-mailed
statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
